structure.unit: Inland Fisheries And Game And Other Natural Resources

law.catch_line: Special Statutes Relating To Fisheries; Alewife Fisheries
law.text: This chapter shall not be deemed to affect any provision or penalty contained, or any privilege granted, in any special statute relating to fisheries in any particular place, nor to any alewife fisheries under the provisions of sections ninety-four to ninety-seven, inclusive, of chapter one hundred and thirty.
